DESCRIPTION:Get ready for a night of laughs and unfiltered conversation at Late Knight! Join us for a moderated Q&A with comedian and writer Caleb Hearon\, known for his sharp wit\, viral sketches\, and unapologetically honest takes on life\, pop culture\, and everything in between.    Caleb has built a massive following through his hilarious social media presence and podcast appearances\, bringing a unique blend of storytelling\, sarcasm\, and chaos that keeps audiences hooked. Whether you’ve seen his viral videos or are just looking for a fun Friday night\, this is your chance to hear directly from one of comedy’s rising voices. 🎤 Event Details Who: @calebsaysthings Where: College Avenue Student Center - MPR  When: Doors Open @ 9:00 PM | Show Starts @ 9:30 PM Co-sponsored with @RUPArutgers    🎟 Important Info Open to Rutgers–New Brunswick students only RSVP required on getINVOLVED — seats are limited!
