DESCRIPTION:For Reading Day\, before the week of final exams\, the Zimmerli opens exclusively for Rutgers students to offer a one-of-a-kind space to study\, discover\, and create in the museum. Free refreshments throughout the day. Open to all current Rutgers’ undergraduate and graduate students. Study in the galleries and enjoy free provided food and refreshments in our lobby as well as a variety of brain break activities! Rutgers student ID required. Visit event page for all details & updates.
